--- tasks [feature] ---
TasksCont  [C]    : Task management routes | $auth → THIS → TasksSer
TasksSer   [S]    : Task management business logic | TasksCont ← THIS → TasksRepo ⇒ EvtTasksChanged
TasksRepo  [R]    : tasks tables, RLS $tenant | TasksSer ← THIS → $db
TasksType  [T]    : Tasks, CreateTasksDto, UpdateTasksDto
TasksVal   [V]    : Zod schemas for tasks input | TasksCont ← THIS
TasksTest  [X]    : unit + integration tests
